records.name: Coco Palm Dhuni Kolhu - 20 Percent Off Roundtrip Seaplane For Stays From 1 May To 30 September 2025

descriptions.direction: Located in Dhunikolhu, Coco Palm Dhuni Kolhu is on a private beach. While the natural beauty of Thulhaadho Beach and Mendhoo can be enjoyed by anyone, those looking for an activity can check out Thulhaadho Harbor. Looking to get your feet wet? Windsurfing and fishing adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Luxurious and unforgettable stay is guaranteed in these tropical-style villas located by the crystal-clear waters of a private island paradise. Opening out to stunning views of the ocean or surrounding greenery, the resort air conditioned villas are equipped with fine wood and cane furnishings. Breathtaking views are to be enjoyed from the private terraces with outdoor seating. The resort features 5 dining options and 5-star Spa and fitness facilities. This is the ideal place for those wishing to practice a wide range of water sports such as canoeing and diving. Alternatively, they can indulge with soothing massages at the Spa.
